Introduction

Eunseok is a South Korean singer under SM Entertainment and a member of the boy group RIIZE. He made his debut on September 4th, 2023, with the single album "Get A Guitar".

Originally introduced as a member of the trainee team SMROOKIES in July of 2022, it was later revealed that he would be a member of SM's new boy group RIIZE in August of 2023.
